categories.name: Store and/or access information on a device
categories.description: Cookies, device identifiers, or other information can be stored or accessed on your device for the purposes presented to you.

categories.name: Select basic ads
categories.description: Ads can be shown to you based on the content you’re viewing, the app you’re using, your approximate location, or your device type.

categories.name: Create a personalised ads profile
categories.description: A profile can be built about you and your interests to show you personalised ads that are relevant to you.

categories.name: Select personalised ads
categories.description: Personalised ads can be shown to you based on a profile about you.

categories.name: Create a personalised content profile
categories.description: A profile can be built about you and your interests to show you personalised content that is relevant to you.

categories.name: Select personalised content
categories.description: Personalised content can be shown to you based on a profile about you.

categories.name: Measure ad performance
categories.description: The performance and effectiveness of ads that you see or interact with can be measured.

categories.name: Measure content performance
categories.description: The performance and effectiveness of content that you see or interact with can be measured.

categories.name: Apply market research to generate audience insights
categories.description: Market research can be used to learn more about the audiences who visit sites/apps and view ads.

categories.name: Develop and improve products
categories.description: Your data can be used to improve existing systems and software, and to develop new products

categories.name: Use precise geolocation data
categories.description: Your precise geolocation data can be used in support of one or more purposes. This means your location can be accurate to within several meters.

categories.name: Actively scan device characteristics for identification
categories.description: Your device can be identified based on a scan of your device's unique combination of characteristics.
